<Link id="l00365" /><CodeLine lineNumber="365"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Symbol resolution interface.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00366" /><CodeLine lineNumber="366"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">///</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00367" /><CodeLine lineNumber="367"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Allows symbol flags and addresses to be looked up by name.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00368" /><CodeLine lineNumber="368"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Symbol queries are done in bulk (i.e. you request resolution of a set of</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00369" /><CodeLine lineNumber="369"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// symbols, rather than a single one) to reduce IPC overhead in the case of</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00370" /><CodeLine lineNumber="370"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// remote JITing, and expose opportunities for parallel compilation.</span></CodeLine>
